@{b}Installation@{ub}
------------

Right then, let's get cracking... first I'll show you a list of all the files
that should have been included in this ASWPOP distribution...

aswpex.ircmsg               1430
aswpex.ftpmail              3544
aswpin.autorep              1019
aswpop                     10574
aswpop.acton                 334
aswpop.history              3045
ftpmail.help                  25
aswpop.prefs                 198
aswpop.guide               30546

If some files are missing, or extra files are present in your archive, then
you have an un-original archive that could be corrupt of virus infected!!
You can get real versions of ASWPOP from most aminet mirrors in comm/tcp, on
the @{"FrostFree BBS " Link "F3"} or my @{"Homepage " Link "ASW"}....

The first thing you should do when installing ASWPOP is deciding where the
bulk of the files are going to go.. I have mine in a ASWPOP directory in
amitcp:, you can stick them anywhere really... the only file that HAS to be
somewhere is aswpop.prefs, which must be stuck in your S: directory!

So copy all the ASWPOP files bar aswpop.prefs to a directory, and remember
where you've put them! :)

Now then, if you so wish, you can use the included installer to install and
ASWPOP, however, if you wish to get your hands dirty with shell operations,
then follow me!..

@{"Return to About " Link "About"} @{" Configuration " Link "Configure"}

@Endnode

@Node "Configure"
